<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ftf-sauce-and-marinating">SAUCE AND MARINATING</h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>While the tofu is cooking, prepare the sauce by mixing everything together. Feel free to adjust to your taste.</li>



<li><strong>Want it really saucy? </strong>You can double the sauce!</li>
</ul>



