<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ftf-cooking-the-shredded-tofu-bulgogi">COOKING THE SHREDDED TOFU BULGOGI</h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>In a medium wok or pan, add in the shredded tofu and sauce. Cook down over medium heat for 7-8 minutes or until the sauce has reduced and absorbed by the tofu. The sauce will also slightly thicken from the sugars in the sauce.</li>



<li>Taste the tofu and feel free to season more, if desired.</li>



<li>Turn off the heat. </li>
</ul>



